snippet.title: Midnight Mercenaries Chapter 1 Playthrough
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage of the first chapter of Midnight Mercenaries, a fangame of mine that mixes Team Fortress 2 with Hotline Miami's gameplay.
▶DOWNLOAD FOR FREE HERE: https://gamejolt.com/games/midnightmercenaries/375928

▶Thumbnail made by Bendroo https://twitter.com/OfficialBendroo

▶Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/GermanPeter
▶Twitter: https://twitter.com/RealGermanPeter
▶Discord: https://discord.gg/WKd9323

0:00 "Full Houses" (Scout)
3:10 "Dead Silent" (Spy)
6:25 "One Shot" (Sniper)
9:14 "Tag Team" (Sniper & Spy)
12:09 "House Demolition" (Soldier & Demo)
16:15 "Over the Tracks" (Pyro)
19:46 "New Friends" (Heavy)

▶Fonts:
"Riffic Free" by Nini Prower

Thanks for coming prepared.
